snippet.title: Thomas and the High Speed Train

localized.description:
The fat controller feels that steam engines are too dirty and the passengers would appreciate a modern, clean and fast replacement, but things don't work out as he had hoped.
Filmed on the Sandwell Valley Railway. For up to date news about the railway visit http://sandwellvalleyrailway.blogspot.co.uk.
